on a transplant list.

360
00:21:40,499 --> 00:21:43,094
Who knows how long
before she gets a viable donation?

361
00:21:43,169 --> 00:21:46,628
Firehouse won't hold her position
until she heals. She'd lose her job.

362
00:21:46,705 --> 00:21:50,369
First you want to treat her like a guinea
pig, now you're concerned about her life?

363
00:21:50,476 --> 00:21:52,342
- You just want to be right.
- And you don't?

364
00:21:55,714 --> 00:21:57,979
Are you going to step in
at any point?

365
00:22:00,853 --> 00:22:03,345
I think Park's idea has
the best chance of success.

366
00:22:04,456 --> 00:22:05,515
Get her prepped.

367
00:22:14,033 --> 00:22:16,332
Do you really think his idea is better,

368
00:22:16,402 --> 00:22:18,962
or do you not wanna look
like you're biased?

369
00:22:20,840 --> 00:22:23,366
I'm not happy
about this situation either,

370
00:22:23,475 --> 00:22:25,205
but you're overreacting.

371
00:22:25,811 --> 00:22:27,211
Get it under control,

372
00:22:27,313 --> 00:22:29,748
or you're watching from the gallery.

373
00:22:44,263 --> 00:22:45,322
Hi.

374
00:22:45,397 --> 00:22:46,490
Hey.

375
00:22:59,411 --> 00:23:02,347
Do you have a problem with me
staying friends with Shaun?

376
00:23:02,414 --> 00:23:05,907
I know you've told him
you're fine with it, but are you?

377
00:23:07,219 --> 00:23:08,380
Yes.

378
00:23:08,454 --> 00:23:09,581
Really?

379
00:23:10,022 --> 00:23:11,957
I mean, I'm totally glad you are.

380
00:23:12,358 --> 00:23:13,358
It's great.

381
00:23:13,792 --> 00:23:16,785
I'm not sure I would be
if I were in your shoes.

382
00:23:18,397 --> 00:23:21,424
If it was any other guy,
I probably wouldn't be.

383
00:23:22,902 --> 00:23:25,667
But Shaun, he always tells the truth.

384
00:23:26,238 --> 00:23:29,766
So when he told me
he's not interested in you, I believe him.

385
00:23:31,543 --> 00:23:32,543
Okay.

386
00:23:39,952 --> 00:23:42,444
You told the residents
not to come to me?

387
00:23:44,423 --> 00:23:46,824
No, that's not at all what I said.

388
00:23:47,192 --> 00:23:48,888
You didn't tell them,

389
00:23:48,961 --> 00:23:51,192
"Next time you have a problem,
come to me directly"?

390
00:23:51,797 --> 00:23:55,791
I was encouraging open communication
and trust on my team.

391
00:23:55,901 --> 00:23:58,097
What I have is ambitious residents

392
00:23:58,203 --> 00:24:02,231
struggling to figure out how to be
cooperative as well as competitive.

393
00:24:02,308 --> 00:24:04,504
