00:24:32,538 --> 00:24:34,973
Are you happy to be going home?

402
00:24:40,279 --> 00:24:41,941
Have any questions for us?

403
00:24:46,285 --> 00:24:47,309
Are you sure?

404
00:24:47,753 --> 00:24:50,245
Because you don't seem happy
to go home.

